{"tid":1786624,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"笑撚死 我同學終於俾人拉撚左","createTime":"2019-12-17T09:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T14:49:43.000Z","uid":40867,"like":35,"dislike":250,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"7cbc4833e4fee39b9c4a501153f3a60e6ef00ac4","tid":1786624,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:19:40.000Z","msg":"條友仔都係個d唔識埋堆嘅毒能黎架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時我同佢都冇乜兩句 不過日日睇佢俾人玩都幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前兩日知道佢俾人拉埋 真係忍唔住笑出聲<br />\n屌原來係學校咁摺 係出面搞埋d咁嘅嘢 反差大到<br />\n個個都估唔到佢咁勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過冇啦 佢咁嘅人去到差館都唔知點挨<br />\n可能過多兩個禮拜就失蹤 講定RIP先都得<br />\n今日同班同學幫佢整埋大頭 比足面架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同往日一樣嘻嘻哈哈咁撚你 啊唔係...係撚你張大頭(咁鬼叫你比人拉咩...一陣咪又話唔同你玩)<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得我地係咪對佢好好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主好嘢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主好嘢"},{"pid":"eb616d5b3b9dc8eb0418adbd828fb1cebf7c8986","tid":1786624,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01dd930408c61520473ee30ebbd9b6134f9a60d2","tid":1786624,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d881536a2146898dc0bd12be846d29a6e40bba","tid":1786624,"uid":40867,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:23:21.000Z","msg":"負皮個d係咪平時冇朋友d毒能黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796ba02a97bf5160970e22171ce6be5ae26b7dfa","tid":1786624,"uid":201568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:26:24.000Z","msg":":<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"h